     MOVE "P-020-03"             TO CASE-ID.                     
     MOVE "あい"  TO GE-03.                                      
     IF GE-03 = "あ０い"                                         
        AND FUNCTION BYTE-LENGTH(GE-03) = 6                      
                                 DISPLAY CASE-ID "OK"            
